Creation of the pastry database for CRUD operations practice!

CREATE TABLE products (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    price NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

-----------------------------------------
Here you insert some pastries for the table :)

